Name: SUPER BOT
About the game: Take part in the adventures of 'SUPER BOT', an action adventure game from a third person perspective. The main character is a cute robot, which, due to the domination of the industrial planet by nasty bugs, sets out to fight to regain energy and save his friends. On the way you will chase worms and fight the guardians to regain energy and save your friends. Features: - Pleasant and addictive gameplay. - Beautiful 3D graphics. - Ability to play via the Xbox controller. - Low minimum hardware requirements. Warning: - SUPER BOT is a short game that takes about 30 minutes to complete - The game does not have a save system
